channel.title: Cannot delete type of file
channel.description:
In my server characters folder, I found some files that are not class, java, cfg, txt, anything. They are named 'File', are 0 bytes, and when I delete them it says:
Cannot delete file: Cannot read from the source file or disk.
I have tried renaming it, a bat file, etc, but nothing works since I don't know what type of file it is. Any help?
I am sorry if this is the wrong section, but it does have to do with my server because it is driving me insane.
-Thanks in return.
